Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{全然力が入ったらん。}I see no power at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{これが全国大会に出場するチームの練習か？}Is this how a team that advanced to All-Japan Tournament practices?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{出場それ以上は優勝せればならん。}You can't rest just because you got elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝を逃がしたら、二位もビリっけつも同じことだ。}When you lose, it doesn't matter if you're placed second or last.
