Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんなXXX正確に行かないわ。}We can't be this precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、どうやって守るんだ？}Then how do you want to defend?
