Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。あたしたちの実力を認められたのね。}Ayuhara-san, looks like our skill didn't go unrecognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{責任重大だは。頑張らなきゃ。}He's counting on us. We cannot let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{これでいい。}It's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{怖いもの知らずのこの自信が、この子達には一番必要なんだ。}They absolutely need to believe in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん！}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、泉さん。}Ah, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{いよいよ明日東京ね。}Tokyo at last, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張ってね。}Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたの分まで頑張るわ。}I'll do my best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん。}Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう。}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたのお陰であたしね、陸上部で最初からやり直す決心をついたのよ。}Thanks to you, I gained my motivation to start over in the track and field club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{きっとやるわ。}I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{それでこそ泉さんよ、本当に良かったわ。}Attagirl, Izumi-san. I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{その代わりにきっと優勝してきてね。}In return, show us a great victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろんそのつもりよ。}That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、全国大会だから、どんな強いチームをXか分からないし。}But we don't know how strong the All-Japan Tournament participants will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫よ。}It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{今のあなたたちだったら、絶対に勝てるわ。}You can totally win with your present form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。頑張るわ。}We'll do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、シューズ。}Ah, my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、先生未だいらしたんですか？}Ah, you still were here, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。んー何だ、鮎原？どうした？}Y-Yeah. What's the matter, Ayuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{シューズを忘れたんです。}I forgot my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原。}Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。なんでしょう。}Sir? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{君はそのシューズで大会に出るのか？}Are you going to use these shoes in the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆は？}And the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{新しいの履くそうです。}I heard they'll wear new shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{いけないでしょうか？こんな古いで試合にでっちゃう。}Is it bad if I show up in such old shoes in the matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{な。}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{履き慣れたシューズの方がよければ、何も履いても構わん。心配か？}If you prefer going out in worn-in shoes, it's all right. Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆はXX自信を持ったようだが、}Everyone seems to have confidence…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{接戦に成った時一番頼りにされるのは…鮎原。君だ。}…but when it comes to close combat, you're the most reliable, Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{戦士はもちろんコーチも最後のワンポイントをキャプテンにかける。}Both players and the coach leave the last point to the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{それがバレーだ。}That's volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいか？}Remember:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{私はコートの外にいると言うことを忘れるな。}I'm always just outside the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、帰って寝ろ。}Go home and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXがいかんぞ。}We can't have you oversleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{セー先生、あたしたちは本当に勝てるでしょうか？}P-Professor, can we really win?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{勝てる。}You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{や、勝てればならん。}Or rather, you must win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{君のその古いシューズと同じように。}You're not unlike those old shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{このボールにも。}And that ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達のXXX必ず勝てる。}If you put forth effort, you can certainly win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{君達は笑えば、このボールも笑う。君達は泣けば、このボールも泣く。}When you laugh, the ball laughs.\NWhen you cry, the ball cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かるか、鮎原？}Do you understand, Ayuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{シューズだけ買えれば、勝てるわけじゃない。}You can't win by buying new shoes alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{ボールだ。このボールだよ。}It's all about the ball. About this ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生。}Professor…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{今夜はぐっすり寝てるんだぞ。}Rest well tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん、遅いはね、鮎原さん。どうしたのかしら。}Ayuhara-san's late. I wonder what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{(XXX・何があった)じゃないでしょうね。}I hope nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{もし間に合わなかったら、一大事よ。}We're screwed if she doesn't make it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{来たわ！}She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、本当。}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん！遅いよ、キャプテン！}– Ayuhara-san!\N– You're late, captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。間に合ってよかったわ。}Ah, I'm glad I made it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{すみません、この子寝坊しちゃって。}We're sorry. She overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{よし。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{これで全員Xな。}Now everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{やれやれ、よかった。}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{では、本郷先生。頼みますよ。}Well then, professor Hongou, I leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、精一杯XXます。}I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{今度の日曜日は僕も応援に行くからね。}I'll come and cheer you on this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{決勝戦まで必ず残ってくれよ。}Be sure to stay in until the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう。ベストを尽くす。}Thank you. We'll try our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原キャプテン。}Captain Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{頼みますよ。}We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{盛大な祝賀パーティーのいよいよ一息Xからな。}We'll hold a huge celebration party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどり。}Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{必ず優勝してくれよ。}Give us splendid victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{こずえ。}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパは仕事の都合で応援に行けられない。テレビで見ているだがな。}Papa's busy with work and won't be able to come. But I'll surely watch you on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。体に気をつけてね。}– Okay.\N– Stay out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。X。}Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張れよ！}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{—富士見学園XXX！\N—頑張って！}– Show what Fujimi Academy is made of!\N– Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{行ってきます。}Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{頑張ります。}We'll do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん！}Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、泉さん。}Ah, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{間に合って良かった。}I barely made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{これ持っててね。}Please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{なにこれ？}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしからプレゼンとよ。}It's a present from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{東京いってから、開けてみて。}Open it when you get to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう。本当にありがとう。}Thank you. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{うれしいわ。}I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、皆さん、頑張ってね。}All right, good luck to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。あなたもね。}Yeah. To you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{元気でね！}Stay safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{行ってきます！}Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{後に時間で東京ね。}We'll be in Tokyo in 2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{何だか胸がドキドキするわ。}My heart is racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ！}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ、やっぱり車は多いね。}As expected, cars are everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{見て！すごいビルね！}Look at all those buildings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、皆。キョロキョロして迷子になるなよ。}Girls, make sure not to get lost while you look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんは一年前までこの東京にいたのね。}Ayuhara-san, you was still here in Tokyo a year ago, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。懐かしいわ。}Yeah. It feels nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{十年ぶり見たいの感じよ。}It feels like it was 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{さて。いいか、諸君。}All right then. Listen, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{修学旅行に来たのではないから、そのつもりで自重するように。}We're not here on a school trip, so show self-restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{大事な試合の前に、食べすぎて体を壊したりしたら、}If you overeat and lose your form before an important match…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{戦士としても最も恥ずかしいことだと言うこと忘れないよ。}…we would extremely embarrass ourselves. Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいな？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{では今から四時間自由行動にする。}Good. The next four hours are leisure time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{門限は四時だ。}The curfew is at six.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{遅れないよな。}Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{わあい！}Waai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{—どうする？\N—銀座行って、買い物XXしたいわ。}– What do we do?\N– Let's go shopping in Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{—ね、あたしたちも銀座へ行けない？\N—いいね。}– Hey, why don't we go see Ginza too?\N– Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生、あの、あたし明法学園へ行ってきたいですけど。}Professor, I want to visit Meihou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほ。}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{君は明法の出身だったな。良かろう。}That's your old school, right? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{明日とは今度の大会でも、優勝候補の呼び声は高いが、}They're one of the favorites in the championships…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、君X遊んできたまえ。}Ah, whatever. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{危ない！}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごい！}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{丸で神業のようだわ。}It was miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{懐かしいだわ。}How nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{この木。}These trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{この花。この(XX地)の匂い。}These flowers. This smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆思いであるわ。}I remember it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、綺麗。}How pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱり来たわね。}You did come here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、吉村さん。}Isn't it Yoshimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{しばらく待ってたのよ。}We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{きっと来てくれると思って。}We knew you'd return some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}My.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたの噂聞いてるわ。}We heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{富士見学園のキャプテンとした張り切ってるんですってね。}You're the enthusiastic captain of Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{久しぶりだから皆に会っていかない？}It's been a long time, why don't we go see the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、今日はちょっと。}But today is—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいじゃないの。さ、コートへ行きましょう。}It's okay! Let's go to the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、ファイトで来ましょう。いい？}Let's do this properly. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、皆さん、鮎原さんよ。}Hey, girls! It's Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ。}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{懐かしい。}We missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{何か元気そうになったじゃない？}She looks more fit, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当。少し太ったみたいね。}Totally. She seems to have gained weight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、そう？どれほどでも。}Is that so? I wonder how much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね。で、今日は早速偵察なの？}You're scouting us out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かってるわよ。}Right on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、ね、何の話？}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{やだ、あなたは何も知らないの？}Wow, you know nothing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんはね、東海代表の富士見学園のメンバーとして上京したのよ。}Ayuhara-san's here as a member of Fujimi Academy, the Toukai's representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、明日から、全国大会に出るの？}So she'll show up in the tournament tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなのよ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆には悪いんだけど、今度は敵味方に分かれて戦えなきゃならないの。}I'm afraid we'll have to fight each other soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ、そうなの？}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは修学旅行とかなんか出ていけかしらと思ったのに。}I thought you were here on a school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{だったら良かったんだけど残念だわ。}Too bad, but that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{それは仕方ないことよ。}It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも名アタッカーのあなたを敵に回すのは脅威ね。}I'd rather avoid having to face a famous attacker like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、そんなこと。}Ah, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちこそ優勝候補のナンバーワンじゃないの。}Same goes for you. Aren't you the tournament's number one favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{それが安心してはいられなくなったの。}I'm not sure about this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうして？}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{思いも寄らない強敵あわれたのよ。}We've met an unexpectedly formidable enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{思いも寄らない強敵？}A formidable enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうなのよ。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{{あなともXXXするといいわ。}I guess there's no harm in warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{今あの体育館の中で練習してるから。}They're in the middle of practice in our gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{おりゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほら、ちくしょう！}Take this, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{この！}You rascal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{何だその恰好は！}What's with your posture!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{あった！}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{おいほら！}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうだ！}What's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{ばかたれ！XXX！}You fool! What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね？すごいでしょう？}They're great, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{吸収の福岡中学だけど、コート貸してあげて吃驚しちゃったわ。}They're Fukuoka Middle School from Kyuushuu. We lend our court to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！回転レシーブ！}Ah! Revolving receive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。あの人だわ。}Hey, it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうだったの。}That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの離れ業は回転レシーブの応用だったんだわ。}She must have used this receive back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{へ？あなたはあの人を知ってるの？}Huh? You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。ちょっと顔見たことがあるだけど。}Nope, I only saw her briefly before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{すごいでしょう?あの人。}She's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{垣之内良子って言う、福岡中のキャプテンよ。}She's Fukuoka's captain, Kakinouchi Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{福岡中の…}Fukuoka, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{確かに、これは強敵だわ。}Indeed, they're a formidable enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうか。福岡中学はね。}Fukuoka Middle School, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの回転レシーブはとても中学生とは思えません。}That revolving receive is way beyond middle schooler level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{それにスパイクとしても、クイック攻撃にしても、}Combined with their spike and quick attack…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{それにスパイクとしても、クイック攻撃にしても、とてもあたしたちにとは立ち位置できそうもありません。}…I don't think we'll be able to stand our ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうかね。}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生、どうしましょう？}What do we do, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちもこれからどこかのコートかれて、練習しましょうか？}Should we find a court somewhere and hold a drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{や、待て。}Nah, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{今更自他又練習しただって始まらん。}It's no use to practice at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{それより、鮎原。}More importantly, Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{その福岡中学のことは皆に話すんじゃないぞ。}Don't tell anyone about Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、こんな心配より、勝つことだ。}Well then. Don't worry. We'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{試合の前にして、悪戯にショックを耐えて、動揺さしては不味い。}We can't lose our spirit before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{福岡中のことはいずれしれると思っただが、知ったのは鮎原でよかった。}Someone had to find out about Fukuoka at some point. I'm glad it was Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{名んなよ、あんたたち！}What's with you girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{何よ？}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{何言ってんのよ？}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{因縁を付けたそっちじゃないのさ？}Haven't {\i1}you{\i0} started it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。あたしたちはただ廊下を歩いてただけだわ。}Yeah. We were only walking down the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{何な言う、ちょっと？}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし(XXXXXX・捕まえにき取ったくせに)。}You shoved my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは吸収代表の福岡中学のもんよ。}We're Kyuushuu's representatives, Fukuoka Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたちも名乗りなさいよ。}How about you introduce yourselves too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{—ちょ—\N—あ、名乗るわよ！}– Hey—\N– Ahh! We'll introduce ourselves all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちはね。東海代表、富士見学園よ。}We're Toukai's representatives, Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{初出場のチームじゃなかね。}Ah, if it isn't the debuting team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{—ハハハ！\N—何ですって！}– Hahaha!\N– What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう一度言ってごらんなさいよ！}Say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{もう勘弁ならないわ。}I can't stand it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{—ちょっと！XXX\N—な—}– Get over here!\N– What—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{—待って！\N—鮎原さん！}– Stop it!\N– Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{みんな、だめよ。こんな所で喧嘩なんかしちゃう。}We can't fight here, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、帰りましょう。}Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもさ、この人達はあんまり失礼なことXXからさ。}But they were so rude to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{失礼はそっちじゃなかったのね。}You were the ones who were rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたたち！止めなさい！}Both of you! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほ！キャプテン！}Ah! Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{大会の試合前に喧嘩XX}What are you doing, fighting before the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{とんでもなか。}How stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、皆部屋へ帰りなさい。}Go back to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{はい。}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{何さ、ギャンギャンと言っていてさ。}What a yapping bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{すみません。あたし、福岡中の垣之内良子です。}Please forgive them. I'm Fukuoka's captain, Kakinouchi Yoshiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{知ってるわ。}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたし、実を言うと、あなたにお目に掛かれ、これで三度目なんですわ。}Actually, this is the third time we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{三度目？}Third time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{一回目は交差点で女の子を助けてあげたあなた。}The first time was when you saved the girl at the crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{二回目は明法学園のコートで練習していたあなた。}The second time was when you practiced in Meihou's court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは富士見学園の鮎原こずえです。}I'm Ayuhara Kozue of Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん。}Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたは。}It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしの名前をご存知？}Do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{もちろん知ってたよ。}Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんたが左右両手を使えるのアタッカーであることも。}You're that ambidextrous attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}My.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうせ明日からの大会でお会いすると思うけど。}We'll probably meet in the tournament anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{その時は、お手柔らかに。}Don't be too hard on me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしの方こそそうお願いしたいわ。}I'd like to ask you the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{垣之内さんってさすがね。}As expected from Kakinouchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{しっかりしてるわ。}She has it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{鮎原さんの名前をちゃんと知ってるなんて。}She properly knew Ayuhara-san's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{んん。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{それだけわがキャプテンの名前は有名なんじゃんよ。}Our captain is famous already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもそれだけじゃないわ。}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの垣之内さんおそらく今度の出場チームの特徴を皆調べたあるんじゃないかしら。}I'm pretty sure Kakinouchi-san researched our debuting team.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{は。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{そう言えばさ、あたしたちの富士見学園(XXX・合併)たら。}Ah, now that I think of it, they seemed to know us Fujimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{フン。}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{初出場のチーム勝って、あの子XXX言ってたわよ。}The braids girl did call us the debuting team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}My.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、皆知ってたんだわ？}So they know us all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{だとすると大変よ。}We're in trouble if they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは初めての出場をXXX他のチームのこと何か全然調べようとしなかったでしょう。}We'll play with them for the first time and we haven't done any research either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生はどうかあしら。}What about professor Hongou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生もそこまで詳しく調べてないみたいよ。}Looks like professor Hongou didn't research them deeply either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{だって、福岡中学のこと知らなかったですもの。}After all, he didn't know about Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{敵を知り己を知れば百戦危うからず。}"Know your enemy, know yourself\Nand you shall not fear a hundred battles."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{よく家の爺ちゃんが言ってたけどさ。}My grandpa used to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{こう言うことなのね。}I guess he was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうね。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{しまった。}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{皆を動揺させてしまったらしいわ。}It seems I've undermined their confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生が恐れてたものはこのことなんだわ。}This is probably what proffesor Hongou feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{大丈夫よ。}It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{結局、実力は第一よ。}In the end, the skill is the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{色んな情報知ってても、力がなければ、勝ってはしないだから。ね？}Had we been weak, all information in the world wouldn't help us win. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。そうよ！}Exactly. Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生はきっと無手勝流で行こうと思っているよ。}Professor Hongou surely wants us to win in our own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちをXXX…}We need to believe…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{いいこと言ってくれるわ、みどりさん。}You said it nicely, Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{その調子よ。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{それより、鮎原さん、出発の時泉さんに何を貰ったの？}By the way, Ayuhara-san, what did you get from Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。忘れてたわ。}Ah, I've forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{えと、どこへ入れれたかしら。}I wonder where I put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{あったわ。}Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{これよ。}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{何がはいてるかしら。}I wonder what she put inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、手帳ね。}Oh. It's a memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{何を書いたあるのかしら。}What's written inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{《全国大会・出場チーム・MEMO》}《All-Japan Tournament debuting teams memo》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}My.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{出場チームのめもだわ。}It's the debuting teams memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝候補チーム\N明法学園（関東）\N福岡中学（九州）\N奥山中学（東北）\N富士見中（静岡）}《Winning candidate teams》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝候補は明法、福岡。}The favorites are Meihou and Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{奥山ね。}And Okuyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{わ、その次は我々の富士見学園ですってさ。}Whoa, our Fujimi's after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんいつのまえにこんなこと調べたのかしら。ね？}I wonder when she did collect this data?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{浜紀中時代に全国大会出てるから、}She must have wanted to enter the tournament back in Hamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{そのころからじゃない？きっと。}That's probably when she started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{いつかこれを役に立ってようと思ってたのね。}There was no telling when it could prove useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{それが自分必要できなくなってので、あたしたちに…}She gave it to us when she no longer needed it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{ありがとう、泉さん。}Thank you, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは必ずあなたの分まで頑張るわ。}We'll work hard for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら。選手名を書いたあるんじゃん？}She wrote the member names too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{明法学園のよしむらさんがとっぷだわ。}Yoshimura-san's the best in Meihou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{やっぱりね。}Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX福岡中の垣之内さんか。}As expected, Fukuoka has Kakinouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、早くそれさっきを見せてよ。}Hurry, show us what's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝選手の特技とその弱点}《Players' strong and weak points》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{よしむらさとみ。サーブの名手。}Yoshimura Satomi. Expert at serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{その豪壮XXサーブは、警戒を要する。}Be cautious when receiving her serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{ただし、レシーブは弱い。}However, she's poor at receiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{したがって明法チームは攻撃が強いが、守りにまあると脆い。}Therefore, Meihou has a strong offensive, but a fragile defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{その通りよ。}I can vouch for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{あそこあたしがいたころからそうだったわ。}Back when I still was there, it held true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{新井和代、X中。フェイントの名手。}Arai Kazuyo, Naniwa Middle School. Expert at feinting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{ブロックの際気をつけること。}Be cautious of her blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{ただし、攻撃が弱い。}However, offensive is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{防御型チーム。}Team focuses on defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{明法とは対照的なチームらしいわね。}They're like Meihou's opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{垣之内良子。福岡中。}Kakinouchi Yoshiko, Fukuoka Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{特には回転レシーブ。}Her specialty is revolving receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、回転レシーブですって！}"Revolving receive", it reads!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？あの人は…}Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:20:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{本当かしら？}I wonder if it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{その回転れシーぶは大学戦士級の正がある。}This revolving receive is an university-level technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{又ライン擦れ擦れに打ち込む、強烈なスパイクも警戒を要する。}Beware her line-grazing hits and intense spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{で、チームの弱点は？}What are their team's weak points?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{このチームは攻撃に防御みた才能技をX持ち—}This team is proficient with both offensive and defensive…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{得に弱点はない。}Weak points: none!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、明法よりもXXXじゃない？}Aren't they way better than Meihou then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、どうしよう？}What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{早く、本郷先生に知らせなくちゃ。}We need to tell professor Hongou at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよ。このメモを先生の所へ。ね、皆。}Yeah. Let's show him this memo. Come on, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。皆で行こうよ。}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{—行こう。\N—その必要がない。}– Go!\N– There's no need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{—先生！\N—本郷先生！}– Professor!\N– Professor Hongou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{本郷先生。}Professor Hongou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{福岡中学のことは、僕もさっき鮎原に聞いたよ。}I already heard about Fukuoka from Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、何がいい作戦が？}Then, what's our strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{ない。}None.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの、それじゃやっぱり無手勝流ですか？}So you really want us to win by ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{と言えば、体裁がいいんだが。}Speaking of, make it look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、はっきり言えば、出たとこ勝負とやつだな。}But I think it's a gamble after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ。}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生！}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{冗談言ってる場合じゃありません。}This is not the time to tell jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうです。}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さんが折角呉れたこの大事なメモ。いかせなくちゃ。}Izumi-san put so much effort into it. We should respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生も、早く読んでみてください。}Professor, please hurry and read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{これです。}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{あ！}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま。}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{いらん。}It's unneeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなものは必要ない。}We don't need such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{先生！}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{そんな酷いこと。}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくら先生でも、酷すぎます。}Professor, you're just too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうよう。あんまりだわ。}Yeah. I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、泉さんはXX可哀想だわ。}All of Izumi-san's effort went down the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{許してくれ、泉。}Forgive me, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{君の好意はありがたいが、}I appreciate your good will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{その好意が私の作戦の邪魔になるのだ。}But that good will clashes with my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{ま、も折角のメモ…}All that information…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{広じゃない！}Don't you pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{資料を読んで勝てるなら、}If you can win with intel alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{コーチを要らんはずだ。}…you don't need a coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{私には私の作戦がある。}I will think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{XXX}You're disappointing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{だまって、私についてこい！}Shut up and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{分かったか？}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{酷い。酷いわ！}That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{いくら何でも、XXXだわ！}You're taking it too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{ああ、折角の貴重の資料。}Ah, all those precious notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{こんなことしちゃってさ。}How could he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{何を考えてるのか、あたしにも分からないわ。}Even I don't know what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あたしたちはただ黙って先生についていけばいいんだわ。}But it should be okay if we just follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうすれば、道が自ずから開ける。}If we do, the road will surely open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{迷ってはいけない。}We can't waver now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{泉さん、見てて。}Izumi-san, just watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたの好意は絶対に無駄にしないわ。}Your good will certainly won't go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝旗は必ずあなたのもとへ持って帰るから。}We'll definitely bring you a splendid victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:56.11,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{福岡中学の垣之内とはなにものか？}What's the deal with Kakinouchi of Fukuoka Middle School?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:24:01.03,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{こずえは福岡中の試合振りをみたいと言うが、本郷コーチは許せなかった。}Kozue wants to research Fukuoka's style, but coach Hongou doesn't let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:02.53,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{いよいよ準決勝。}Finally, the semifinals.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:05.99,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{富士見学園は「木の葉落とし」でXXX勝ち越しをあげた。}Fujimi Academy keeps winning with the "Leaf Fall" technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:10.12,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{次は名門明法学園対福岡中学の試合だ。}The next game is the prestigious Meihou Academy versus Fukuoka Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:14.46,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{だが、本郷コーチは試合を見せず、代わりに音楽を聞かせて。}But Hongou, rather than taking the girls to see the match, makes them listen to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.46,0:24:19.30,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{その頃、コートでは明法学園が目を覆いたくなる、試合を展開していた。}Meanwhile the game was unfolding with Meihou girls wanting to avert their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:22.67,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
